verse.lines:
{lang-eng}My soul longs, yes even faints;
For Your courts, Lord, I supplicate.
Even birds have found a home
Among Your altars, at Your throne.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Blessed is the man dwelling in Your house;
He’ll still be praising with his mouth.
Blessed is the man who’s strong in You;
To Zion he will make it through.{/lang-eng}
